research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Wortham town, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro Tem, and four Council Members. Patty Jones is the current Mayor. Michael Busby serves as Mayor Pro Tem and a Council Member. Jeff Carr, Cliff NeSmith, Patrick Evans, and Deborah Evans are listed as Alderpersons, which are equivalent to Council Members. Some council member terms were noted to expire in 2026, with elections for these positions scheduled for May 2026.
